::Ender::
       "A puddle you say?"  He hauls himself out of the wrecked ship.  "Sorry 
about that, ya know, the whole blowing things up took a lot out of my poor 
ship. "  He sighs.  "So you're a predacon eh?  I'm ... welll ... I'm me."  He 
nods amicably, "I serve no one ... well ... actually I used to but now I 
don't."
